data.description: This charming home offers a delightful blend of comfort and functionality, featuring a thoughtful  floorplan designed for modern living.Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the inviting ambiance that defines this residence. With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, there's ample space for the entire family to enjoy. The layout is thoughtfully designed to maximize both privacy and togetherness. The heart of the home lies in its spacious living areas, where natural light pours in, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen, equipped with all stainless steel appliances offer a space to cultivate your culinary skills.This home also features a fully fenced in backyard to make your outdoor living space of your dreams! ROOF 2021!
